        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e108">Rubrica 30</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De peccato et peccatoribus consideratione religiosa</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e114">
           De peccato et peccatoribus 
           <lb ed="#O"/>consideratione religiosa. Rubrica 30
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e121">
           <lb ed="#O"/>PSalmista. i pslamus ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e125">beatus uir qui
           non abiit in consilio impiorum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et in uia peccatorum non stetit.</quote>
           <pb ed="#O" n="24-r"/>
           <cb ed="#O" n="a"/>
           <lb ed="#O"/>et <unclear>cr.</unclear>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e139">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e134">psalmus. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e141">Qui diligit iniquitatem 
           <lb ed="#O"/>odit animam suam.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e148">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e145">36 psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e150">Considerat 
           <lb ed="#O"/>peccator iustum et querit mortificare 
           <lb ed="#O"/>eum dominus autem non derelinquet eum in manibus 
           <lb ed="#O"/>eius.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e158">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e159">SA<!--line bumps up-->lomon in prouer. capitulo 23. <!--line bumps back down--> </ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e162">Ne emu<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>letur 
           cor tuum peccatores sed in 
           <lb ed="#O"/>timore dei esto tota die quia ha<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>bebis 
            spem in nouissimo et prestolatio tu<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>a 
            non auferetur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e172">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e175">Tobie hystoria <!--line bumps up--> capitulo 12.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e176">Qui faciunt <!--line bumps back down--> peccata et iniquitatem
           <lb ed="#O"/>hostes sunt animae sue.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e182">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e187">IEsus filius sirach <!--line bumps up--> in eccl. capitulo 5. <!--line bumps back down--> </ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e186">Non ad<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dicias
            peccatum super peccatum
            <lb ed="#O"/>et ne dicas miseratio dei magna 
            <lb ed="#O"/>est multudi peccatorum meo<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>rum 
            miserebitur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e194">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e199">capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e196">Non celas
           <lb ed="#O"/>gloriam et opes peccatoris non enim 
           <lb ed="#O"/>scis quae futura sit illius subuersio.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e204">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e213">Mattheus in euan. capitulo 19</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e208">Iesus dixit
           non homicidium facies non adul<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>terabis 
           non facies furtum non falsum te<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>stimonium 
           dices.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e217">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e230">Iohannes in euan. <!--line bumps up--> capitulo i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e221">Si dixerimus <!--line bumps back down--> peccatum non habemus 
           <lb ed="#O"/>ipsi nos seducimus et ueritas in nobis 
           <lb ed="#O"/>non est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e229">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e242">capitulo 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e231">Omnis qui facit pec<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>catum
           seruus est peccati.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e237">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e252">capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e239"> Si ce<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ci 
           essetis non haberetis peccatum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e245">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e262">Idem 
           <lb ed="#O"/>capitulo 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e247">Omnis qui facit peccatum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et iniquitatem facit et peccatum iniquitas 
           <lb ed="#O"/>est. ¶ Qui facit peccatum ex diabolo est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e255">
           <lb ed="#O"/> ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e274">capitulo 5.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e257">et fine Omnis iniquitas peccatum est
           <lb ed="#O"/>et est peccatum ad mortem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e265">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e290">Idem epistola. 
           <lb ed="#O"/>2. capitulo unico.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e267">Qui facit peccatum non ui<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>det 
           deum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e274">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e303">Iudas <!--line bumps up--> alphei apostolus qui fuit frater <!--line bumps back down--> iacobi apostoli epistola vnica. capitulo 2. et fine</ref> 
           <cb ed="#O" n="b"/>
           <lb ed="#O"/> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e278">Peccatores impii hi sunt mur<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>muratores
           querulosi secundum desideria 
           <lb ed="#O"/>sua ambulantes et os illorum loquitur 
           <lb ed="#O"/>superbiam mirantes personas questus causa.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e290">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e322">Iacobus apostolus epistola unica. capitulo i.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e294">Peccatum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>cum consummatum fuerit generat mortem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e300">
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e332">capitulo 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e302">Scienti bonum facere et non faci<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>enti 
           peccatum est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e308">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e344">Paulus apostolus e<!--line bumps up-->pistola. i. ad corinthios. capitulo 10. <!--line bumps back down--> </ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e312">Non potestis men<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>se 
           dei participes esse et mense de<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>moniorum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e320">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e356">capitulo 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e322">Stimulus mortis 
           <lb ed="#O"/>peccatum est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e328">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e368">Seneca <!--line bumps up--> epistolarum ad lucillum libro 17 <!--line bumps back down--> capitulo 2. </ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e332">Omnibus crimen suum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>uoluptati est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e339">
           <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e343">Idem de moribus. 
           <lb ed="#O"/>Omne peccatum actio est uoluntaria.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e349">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e392">Isydorus soliloquiorum libro 2. capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e353">
           Sepe occasio peccandi uoluntatem 
           <lb ed="#O"/>facit.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e365">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e410">MA<!--line bumps up-->theus uindocinensis in poetria <!--line bumps back down--> particula. i. capitulo 6.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e369">Peccatum gemi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>nat 
           peccantis gloria: culpam. Di<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ffamat fama dissipentis honor.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e379">
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Rd1e425">capitulo 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e381">Uenialis est peccandi incidentia sed 
           <lb ed="#O"/>criminalis peccandi frequentia.</quote>
        </p>
      </div>
